{"tid":629206,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遇襲水晶店東親述： 攞鏹水向我塊面係咁潑","createTime":"2018-04-14T13:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T13:34:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a670a5905a002784b4b2d7c819038be42f7bd4d7","tid":629206,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361616?_ga=2.37398176.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361616%3F_ga%3D2.37398176.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=B00LNoCgMr4boGkBCs%2BB%2BaEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5b6edd2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361616%3F_ga%3D2.37398176.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=275d674a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361616?_ga=2.37398176.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n遇襲水晶店東親述：<br />\n攞鏹水向我塊面係咁潑<br />\n<br />\n2.4K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗西九龍中心水晶店東主，前晚遭神秘女子淋腐液。《蘋果》記者聯絡到傷者，他指眼睛被淋中，現時要食藥滴眼水治理，但視力還是模糊不清，擔心康復進度。至於遇襲原因，他表示完全沒頭緒。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水晶店昨日沒有開門，中午時份，記者電話聯絡到仍在留醫的傷者林先生(57歲)。他表示，警方昨早也到病房向他了解情況。他憶述說，前晚7時50分左右，「有個女人，戴黑色口罩，穿黑色衫黑色褲入嚟。我諗住有客人，就問有啲咩幫到佢，點知佢攞支好似鏹水嘅嘢向我塊面係咁潑」。<br />\n<br />\n女子得手後即逃走，但「一路走一路潑，我追出去，攞個石榴掟佢。跟住自己衝入廁所洗眼」，他不肯定是否鏹水，但「件衫出煙」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林目前留院治理，「洗眼兩次，食藥滴眼藥水，但睇野好濛，不停流眼水」。他指當時看不清楚對方樣貌，「佢有備而來，我專心做緊嘢」。"},{"pid":"275e558917fe435055576d1e128cf034b4ffb9e4","tid":629206,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T13:34:09.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}